      "file_path": "catalog-be/src/main/java/org/openecomp/sdc/be/components/impl/ResourceImportManager.java",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 204,
      "message": "Split this method:\npublic void importAllNormativeResource(final String resourcesYaml, final NodeTypesMetadataList nodeTypesMetadataList, final User user, final boolean createNewVersion, final boolean needLock)\nand \npublic void importAllNormativeResource(final  Map<String, Object> nodeTypesYamlMap, final NodeTypesMetadataList nodeTypesMetadataList, final User user, final boolean createNewVersion, final boolean needLock)\nThe first method above will call the second method and the second method shall also be called from SericeImportBusinssLogic so there is no need to convert the nodeTypesToCreate to a String and back again",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5269,
        "name": "Michael Morris",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "michael.morris@est.tech",
        "username": "MichaelMorris"
      },
      "updated": "2022-08-08 14:15:01.000000000",
